title: Neff at Superpark 2013
description: Superpark believe it or not has been going on for 17 years, but this was the first one for Neff and some of the team riders. Mt. Bachelor outside of Bend, Oregon was the host this year, and some of the biggest features to date were built by park crews from around the country. 200 invited pros had the week to show off with plenty of cameras, editors, and team managers to impress. Neff riders: Tim Humphreys, Brandon Davis, Sam Hulbert, Brandon Reis, Nicki Weiss, Dylan Thompson, and Nick Poohachoff had a great showing and we got the footage to prove it!
